      "parse_status": "ok",
      "raw_text_preview": "MOIL LIMITED\n(A Government Undertaking)\n13 MOIL MOIL Bhawan, 1A, Katol Road, Nagpur-13\nqrTN 0712 - 2806100, 2806194 PHONE: 0712 - 2806100, 2806194\n- noor@moil.nic.in E-mail: noor@moil.nicin\ndaige www.moil.nic.in Website: www.moil.nic.in\nCIN No.:L99999MH1962GO1012398 YEARS oF CIN No. : L99999MH1962GO1012398\nERRATINO\nTNE NANAT\nGSTN: 27AAACM8952A1Z1L GSTN: 27AAACM8952A1ZL\nNo. MKTG/51/EMD/2026-27 /Q1\nApril-01, 2026\nM/s\nSub: Price of Electrolytic Manganese Dioxide (EMD) with effect from\n01-04-2026.\nDear Sir,\nWe are pleased to inform you that the price of Electrolytic Manganese\nDioxide (EMD) w.e.f. 1# April, 2026, is as per the details given below:\n1 PRODUCT SPECIFICATION: (INDICATIVE)\nSpecifications\nTest\nMn02 91.00 %\nMoisture 2.50 % Max.\nPH 5.80 Min.\nIron (Fe) 100 PPM\nLead (Pb) 550 PPM\nCopper (CU) 3 PPM\nVoltage 1.70 Volt\n100 # - 99.00 %\nParticle Size\n325 # - 75.00%\n2 PRICE:\nThe Basic Price of EMD would be 1,80,000/ - (One Lakhs Eighty\nThousand) per M.T., GST & other Taxes would be extra as applicable.\nThe price is F.O.R. Dongri Buzurg Mine, Dist.; Bhandara - Maharashtra\nState.\nAdding Strength to steel\nPage 1 of 3\nMOIL LIMITED\n(A Government Undertaking)\n4İUG Hq, 1 et , 9 - 13 MOIL MOIL. "
